  "prompt": "Where can I download \"The Manhattan GRE set of 8 strategy guides\"?",
  "response": "You can find \"The Manhattan GRE Set of 8 Strategy Guides\" available for purchase or download from several platforms:\n\n1. **Manhattan Prep's Official Website**: The best place to start is the official Manhattan Prep website, where you can purchase physical copies or eBooks of the guides.\n\n2. **Amazon**: You can often find both new and used copies of the guides on Amazon. They may also have Kindle versions available for download.\n\n3. **Barnes & Noble**: Check their online store for both physical and digital versions of the guides.\n\n4. **eBook Retailers**: Websites like Google Play Books or Apple Books may offer digital versions for download.\n\n5. **Local Libraries**: Some local libraries offer access to educational resources, including GRE preparation materials. You can check if they have physical or digital copies available for borrowing.\n\nAlways ensure that you are downloading from legitimate sources to avoid copyright issues.",
